#: ../../GoogleTest_Sphinx/source/docs/gmock_cook_book.md:2104
#, python-brace-format
msgid "Setting the Default Value for a Return Type {#DefaultValue}"
msgstr "Impostazione del Valore di Default per un Tipo Restituito {#DefaultValue}"

#: ../../GoogleTest_Sphinx/source/docs/gmock_cook_book.md:2106
msgid ""
"If a mock method's return type is a built-in C++ type or pointer, by "
"default it will return 0 when invoked. Also, in C++ 11 and above, a mock "
"method whose return type has a default constructor will return a default-"
